author: stefan2
msg: Further reduce the costs of creating a svn_fs_x__revision_file_t.
We will often not need to access it due to caching.
(svn_fs_x__revision_file_t): Add OWNER pool and create the local POOL
only lazily.  This saves time and RAM.
auto_open): Use the new utility to access the file pool.
